---
title: Veggie Gyozas & Homemade Crispy Chilli Oil with Sesame Rainbow Salad & Coriander
description: It’s dumpling night! Tender veggie gyozas are paired with a vibrant sesame rainbow salad and a sprinkle of fresh coriander. But wait, there’s more: homemade crispy chilli oil is the ultimate flavour bomb condiment. Put them together and you’ve got a meal that’s fresh, fiery, and full of fun in every bite!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
